- **Secure Credential Creation**: Institutions can issue tamper-proof digital credentials
- **Comprehensive Information Storage**: Stores student details, degree information, graduation year, and institution data
- **IPFS Integration**: Support for additional document storage via IPFS hash
- **Batch Processing Ready**: Designed to handle multiple credential issuances efficiently

### ‚úÖ Instant Verification
- **Real-time Verification**: Instant verification of credential authenticity and validity
- **Global Accessibility**: Verify credentials from anywhere in the world without intermediaries
- **Detailed Credential Information**: Access complete credential details including issuing institution verification
- **Fraud Prevention**: Blockchain immutability ensures credentials cannot be forged or altered

### üîê Security & Control
- **Access Control**: Multi-level permission system (Admin, Institution, Public)
- **Credential Revocation**: Institutions can revoke credentials if necessary (e.g., academic misconduct)
- **Transparency**: All transactions and credential issuances are recorded on blockchain
- **Data Integrity**: Cryptographic security ensures data cannot be manipulated

### üìä Analytics & Tracking
- **Student Portfolio**: Students can view all their credentials in one place
